====Spelling note====
The spelling "[[theatre]]" is the main spelling in Commonwealth English, with "[[theater]]" being rare. 

In United States English, "[[theatre]]" is most often used to refer to the dramatic arts featuring live performances and the associated building, whereas "[[theater]]" refers to prerecorded performances and is synonymous with cinema.

